subject: I received a long and strang mesage about the number Seven
author: Kristin
full_text:
It is over 10mb so I put it on my ESNIPS page to listen if you would
like. 
http://www.esnips.com/doc/2e9d5bd0-a3cf-48f4-bb18-7de47e02029f/Seven-meaning
Below is my transcript of what I heard.  Some of it is rough.. but
those with the patience might want to give it a try... :-)

Here is what I believe the said about the number 7 (secs are cued to
help follow):
